Title: Once tebrik!
Review: Tebrikler! Singapurâ€™dan sonra olcek dusunuldugunde gayet iyi is cikarilmis! GIS ekibini ve yazilim ekibini kutlarim. Yalniz analizlerde lejant onemli. Herkes anlayamaz bu sekliyle mekansal bilgiyi. Bir guncelleme ile lejant eklemek iyi olur! Bir de mekansal sorgulama uygulama uzerinde gec yanit veriyor. Bunu da yazilim ekibi halledebilir saniyorum (boyle buyuk bir veri seti ile calisinca normal tabi) bir onerim de mumkunse raster veriyle sorgulama yaptirabilmek. Mekansal cozunurluk GE goruntulerinde nispeten daha iyi. Vektor uzerinde sorgulama hafif kaliyor. Tesekkurler! Emeginize saglik. Mumkun oldugunca evlerdeyiz! Kolay gelsin.
Title Review: First greeting! Congratulations! Well done  considering the size after Singapore! Congratulations to the GIS team and software team. Legend matters in analysis alone. Not everyone can understand spatial information in this form. It would be good to add legends with an update! Also  the spatial inquiry gives a late answer on the application. I think the software team can handle this too (normal when working with such a large data set). The spatial resolution is comparatively better on GE images. Questioning on the vector remains light. Thank you! Good for your work. We are at home whenever possible! Good luck with.

Title Review:
Some dysfunction. When we select an option other than I am very good in the testing part of the application  the next question has a limited number of options and there is no choice to be made if none of them are available. The only option is to exit the application or choose another option.
So for example; We chose the `` I'm a little tired '' option. In the next question  there are options such as dry cough  fever  etc. However  considering the different effects of the virus from person to person  it is likely that none of them will exist  but there is no such option.
It also shows the risk situation of the location we are on on the map  but it probably shows it on a city / district basis  because as far as I know  the number of people who are positive in the neighborhood where I live is about 2-3  it is very far from me  but it shows the location of my house very risky  but it also shows it very risky in the city center  so there is inconsistency. The map is dysfunctional anyway  certain parts of the country do not say something that we do not know is too risky and thus it becomes dysfunctional. Perhaps  neighborhood-neighborhood risk groups can be created by reducing this to local. In my opinion  this will be a more functional application.

Title Review:
Hello About Hayat Eve Fitting Application 
I would like to ask you the first 10 questions that come to my mind about this application.
1. What provides the infrastructure of this application?
2. Where are the entered and automatically collected data stored on the servers?
3. I couldn't find the privacy policy when we wanted to download from the Apple store. Why is there a clarification text under the title of privacy policy prepared in accordance with KVKK instead of the policy?
4. Why is only article 6/3 specified as a legal reason  although there are personal data that should be processed according to both article 5 and 6 under the heading "purposes" in the disclosure text?
5. According to Article 6/3  only "persons under the obligation to keep secret" can process health data without consent. Is there a confidentiality obligation for the team that can access data by developing this application and providing technical support? What law  if any  arise?
6. The name and phone information of the users' relatives is requested in the application. What is the legal basis for a right to receive personal data belonging to another individual from a User? Is there any information about the legal reason of this situation in the clarification text?
7. For the application  it says "The application can access the location even if the location information is turned off" in the apple store. But most people download the app without knowing it. Wouldn't the person who closed the Location information with the thought that it would be safe actually used his right in article 11? is it legal to continue processing location information despite this?
8. There is a clarification text in the application  but there are no policies such as "Data retention and destruction policy"  "Special Quality Personal Data Processing Policy". Do you have policies? If yes  why not shared?
9. Do you have a data inventory?
10. There is a clarification text in the application but I could not find the clarification text on the Ministry of Health website. Do you not process any other personal data other than those specified in this application? (For example  my IP information when I enter the website of the Ministry or my contact information when I contact the Ministry  etc.)

Thank you very much in advance for your answers.

Stay healthy.

Stay well.

Title: Hatalar cok
Review:
Ailem kisminda kimseyi goremiyoruz. Ekleme yapmis, karsi tarafinda beni eklemis olmasina ragmen karsilikli veri paylasimi olmuyor. Ya da iki ayri kiside program yuklu olmasina ragmen birbirimizi ekleyemiyoruz dolayisiyla karsilikli bolgelerimizi goremiyoruz. Cok fazla kasiyor uygulama. Bir cok kisi daha kayit esnasinda giris/kayit bile yapamiyor. Madem boyle birsey yapildi hakkini vererek tamamlayin acilen. Kisi ekle bolumunde surekli hata verip islem basarili dedigi halde ya eklemeyi yapmiyor birkac kez deniyorsunuz. Yada programi tekrar actiktab sonra ekliyor yada eklemiyor. Kendi bolgeni gormen haricinde diger bolgeleri de gorebilmek cok onemli diye dusunuyorum
